00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,240
A twist of fate.
命运的转折。

185
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,240
Great.
太好了。

186
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:39,240
On a happier note, let's listen to the dialogue a third time.
说点开心的，让我们再听一遍对话。

187
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:41,120
I'm so relieved that your ankle wasn't broken.
我很庆幸你的脚踝没有骨折。

188
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:43,920
I feel just awful about this whole thing.
我对整件事感到非常抱歉。

189
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:44,920
I want to make it up to you.
我想补偿你。

190
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:47,200
Let me take you out to dinner tonight, my treat.
今晚让我带你出去吃饭，我请客。

191
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,800
Oh, that sounds great.
哦，听起来不错。

192
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,520
I'd love to.
我很乐意。

193
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,520
Here's my address.
这是我的地址。

194
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:57,520
Pick me up at eight?
八点来接我？

195
00:08:57,520 --> 00:09:00,520
Perfect.
完美。

196
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:08,680
Thank you for such a lovely evening.
谢谢你让我度过这么美好的夜晚。

197
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:11,560
The food was amazing and I had a great time.
食物很棒，我玩得很开心。

198
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,560
Me too.
我也是。

199
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:14,960
You look so beautiful tonight.
你今晚看起来真美。

200
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,680
I wish this night would never end.
我希望这个夜晚永远不会结束。

201
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,920
There's something that I have to tell you.
有件事我得告诉你。

202
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:19,920
But what is it?
什么事？

203
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:26,360
I woke up today thinking that this would be just like any other day, but I was wrong.
今天醒来时，我以为这会是平凡的一天，但我错了。

204
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,120
The twist of fate brought us together.
命运的转折让我们相遇。

205
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:32,760
I crashed into your life and you into mine and this may sound crazy, but I'm falling
我闯入了你的生活，你也闯入了我的生活，这听起来可能很疯狂，但我正在

206
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:49,640
in love with you, Veronica.
爱上你，维罗妮卡。

207
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:51,200
Okay so we're back.
好了，我们回来了。

208
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:56,160
Erika, I know you have a story of a twist of fate in your life.
埃里卡，我知道你生活中有一个命运的转折故事。

209
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,160
Yes.
是的。

210
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:59,000
Recently, actually, this happened.
实际上，最近就发生了这样的事。

211
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:05,080
I went to this party and at the party there was a contest, like sort of a lottery.
我去参加了一个派对，派对上有一个比赛，有点像抽奖。

212
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:10,160
You could buy some tickets and win a prize and the prize was a week-long vacation.
你可以买些票来赢取奖品，奖品是一周的假期。

213
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:15,600
So I went with some friends of mine and they were tired so they left early and they gave
我和几个朋友一起去的，他们累了就先走了，并把

214
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,600
me their tickets.
他们的票给了我。

215
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,880
And guess what happened?
猜猜发生了什么？

216
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:19,880
What happened?
发生了什么？

217
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,880
We won.
我们赢了。

218
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:22,360
We won the week-long vacation.
我们赢得了一周的假期。

219
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,360
Wow.
哇。

220
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,360
Yeah, it was amazing.
是啊，太棒了。

221
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:27,560
So that was a really lucky twist of fate for me.
所以对我来说，这真是一个幸运的命运转折。

222
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:28,560
A lucky twist of fate.
一个幸运的命运转折。

223
00:10:28,560 --> 00:10:29,560
That's a good story.
这是个好故事。

224
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:30,560
Yeah.
是啊。

225
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:33,560
I'm sure it wasn't that good of a twist of fate for your friends.
我敢肯定，对你的朋友们来说，这个命运转折可没那么好。

226
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:37,200
Yeah, but they were very generous and let me have the prize anyway.
是啊，但他们很大方，还是让我拿走了奖品。

227
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,200
All right.
好吧。

228
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:43,080
Well, we want to hear your stories of maybe some type of twist of fate that you've had.
我们想听听你们的故事，也许是一些你们经历过的命运转折。

229
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,080
Yes.
是的。

230
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:47,920
Maybe love stories, maybe tragic stories, any story.
也许是爱情故事，也许是悲剧故事，任何故事都行。

231
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:54,000
So be sure to leave your questions and comments and your stories at our website, EnglishPod.com
所以一定要在我们的网站 EnglishPod.com 上留下你们的问题、评论和故事，

232
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:58,080
and where you can also find us to answer any questions or doubts.
你也可以在那里找到我们，解答任何问题或疑惑。

233
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,480
Yes, that's right.
是的，没错。

234
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:28,400
So I guess until then, it's goodbye.
那么我想，直到下次，再见。
